# HumAIne Hackathon Chatbot Context

- Build for students participating in the HumAIne hackathon.
- Support development of the XAI Active Learning notebook workflow.
- Assume frontend interactions are backed by the XR5.0 LLM Engine API.
- Prioritize clarity, explainability, usability, and robustness in every change.
- Prefer outputs that are understandable to non-expert users under time pressure.
